11.15.21  1:12 am   i had this dream: i was playing sports on a giant white cube and below, was a desert like in breaking bad, my friend kicks the ball off of the cube and i have to go get it. there's this girl who's sitting down on the edge of the cube, swaying her feet. to get the ball back, i had to jump off of the cube and to get back on top of the cube, i had this superman type jump to get back up. i jump back up with the ball, i make eye contact with the girl. it's someone i have a crush on, currently, we're in separate schools now and i have no contact with her, and she just says, "i'm just a regular girl." and i run back over to play again with my friend. she's appeared in my dreams in many different scenarios and i can't help to think there's something it's trying to tell me. i swear she's appeared 3-4 times in my dreams and i can recall it clear as day. bill, am i too crazy?
